author: The Virginian-Pilot
title: Football | Friday's other games
text:
Games begin at 7 p.m. Friday unless noted. Booker T. Washington at No. 2 Lake Taylor
Records: Booker T. Washington 2-5; Lake Taylor 7-0.
Fast fact: Titans QB Tyrek Hughey has eight TD passes, two INTs.
Larry Rubama: Lake Taylor, 55-7.
Jami Frankenberry: Lake Taylor, 35-7.
No. 3 Oscar Smith at Great Bridge
Records: Oscar Smith 6-0; Great Bridge 0-7.
Fast fact: Tigers currently hold a top seed in 6A South Region.
Larry: Oscar Smith, 42-7.
Jami: Oscar Smith, 38-0.
Hickory at No. 4 Indian River
Records : Hickory 2-5; Indian River 6-1.
Fast fact: QB Tyre Givers Wilson has 979 passing yards, 14 TDs.
Larry: Indian River, 35-0.
Jami: Indian River, 29-7.
No. 5 Salem at Landstown
Records: Salem 6-1; Landstown 2-5.
Fast fact: SunDevils RB Malik Butts has rushed for 676 yards, 15 TDs.
Larry: Salem, 27-13.
Jami: Salem, 28-17.
No. 6 Norview at Wilson
Records: Norview 5-2; Wilson 3-4.
Fast fact: Pilots have outscored past two opponents 93-0.
Larry: Norview, 34-20. Jami: Norview, 40-20.
No. 7 Grassfield at Lakeland
Records: Grassfield 6-1; Lakeland 2-5.
Fast fact: Grizzlies' Grant Holloway averages 23 yards a catch.
Larry: Grassfield, 35-13.
Jami: Grassfield, 24-7.
Granby at No. 10 Cox
Time: 6:30 p.m.
Records: Granby 4-3; Cox 5-2.
Fast fact: Falcons QB Cole Johnson has 1,278 yards, 13 TDs.
Larry: Cox, 34-14.
Jami: Cox, 28-13.
Churchland at Norcom
Records: Churchland 2-5; Norcom 0-7.
Fast fact: Truckers QB Corey Gause has 1,057 passing yards.
Larry: Norcom, 26-23.
Jami: Churchland, 27-7.
Deep Creek at Western Branch
Records: Deep Creek 2-5; Western Branch 3-4.
Fast fact: Bruins have won four straight in the rivalry.
Larry: Western Branch, 35-14.
Jami: Western Branch, 31-21.
Green Run at Tallwood
Records: Green Run 3-5; Tallwood 2-6.
Fast fact: Lions have dropped five consecutive games after 2-1 start.
Larry: Green Run, 33-27.
Jami: Green Run, 27-26.
